		<a name="1093"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#003333"><b>Renegade's Language Faire-Tues, March 13-9PM EST</b></a><br>
		<!--[ <a href="./default.asp?newscomment=1&comments=&url=&news_id=1093&TopicSubject=Renegade's Language Faire-Tues, March 13-9PM EST"><font face="arial" size="1" color="#AAAAAA"> Comments</font></a> ] -->
		<font face="arial" size="1" color="#AAAAAA"> 1:07PM EST - Cymric<br>
		<blockquote>
		<div align="justify"><font face="arial" size="-1" color="#303030">Have you ever wanted to learn Elder Dragon? Wondered what exactly those halflings were saying about you on the crowded pod lift to Kelethin? Have you ever had a burning desire to really get to know the gnolls of Infected paw speaking their tongue fluently?<BR><BR>On behalf of myself and The Renegades, I would like to invite all adventurers of Norrath to join me in a Language Faire! Together meet new people, tell our tales, and increase our knowledge of the many cultures that populate the world of Norrath. <BR><BR>The get together will begin at approximately 9PM EST in the tunnel from EC to North Ro, on the North Ro side. Feel free to bring friends! The Faire is set to last one hour, unless a desire to stay longer is expressed. If so it will certainly be extended! Any questions can be directed to myself in game (Feel free to send a tell) and RSVP's can be posted here. Please include what languages you might be sharing with us and those you express a desire to learn  I will try to match you up with others who have the languages you need/want. <BR><BR>I look forward to seeing you there!<BR><BR>-Kie<BR><BR>(End Note: I know this is something that had been done before, and I really don't remember who had hosted it previously (It was on the old boards  ) - but it's something I would like to get started again on a semi regualr basis - perhaps once per month. If the person who had initially sponsored this is still out there and would like to team up on this, I would very much welcome hearing from you!)<BR><BR><BR><BR>-= Kierya Darkvow =-<BR>-=Renegade Cleric of Innoruuk - 38th season=-<BR></div><br>
			
			Thanks <a href="mailto:" class="news">Kierya</a>!<br>
			
