		<font face="arial" size="1" color="#AAAAAA">12:56PM EST - Kadafi Oakbane<br>
		<blockquote>
		<div align="justify"><font face="arial" size="-1" color="#303030">http://eq.guildmagic.com/ is a system for helping Everquest players and their guild masters to keep useful and accurate lists of their guild members, their levels and their skills. <BR><BR>Guild leaders will love GuildMagic because they no longer need to make endless changes to their guild roster to keep it up to date. Guild members are responsible for keeping their own character details up to date. <BR><BR>Guild members will love GuildMagic because managing your characters is easy and GuildMagic allows you to find other characters on your server with a similar level, race, class or timezone. You can even use GuildMagic to find players on your server with trade skills you need! </div><br>
			
